dBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T14:37:48.000Z","msg":"今日收報30,595.42, 已經穿左100天線31184.23<br />\n但未穿100天線29534,28<br />\n而仲未穿250天線(牛熊市分辦指標)27105.02<br />\n如果純以技術指標來講, 明天穿100天線, 已經可以說初步步入熊市. 當然要真正確認是50天線<br />\n但穿50天線才走, 到時已經成身血<br />\n<br />\n至於壞消息, 是事後吹出來<br />\n當然原因也是事後吹出來<br />\n在當時那一刻是無法知道的<br />\n<br />\n大市曾經上過最高點33484.07, 超越07年高位<br />\n而且也全民瘋狂, 全民皆股<br />\n交投活躍, IPO一上市升好多<br />\n已經構成牛市3期末段的現象"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:02:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大戶為左散貨，搵打手叫人撈底/入貨，正仆街<br />\n現在100天線已穿，初步步入熊市<br />\n牛3已過：歷史創左新高，新股核爆，全民皆股，交投活躍<br />\n<br />\n熊市策略是清倉等時機<br />\n死守甚至撈底都仆硬街</blockquote>咁快想見底</blockquote>Lok sir 求下你再唱好股市同內房好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLok sir 求下你再唱好股市同內房好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da717f13f64467a36b49889fb890fdb6fc756193","tid":552531,"uid":13428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:38:41.000Z","msg":"樂觀sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0e3fc90e04bebcc0ee5935a573affb305fdbbe","tid":552531,"uid":44798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T20:54:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c3b26a629191c35667317af0688b3b19ddc5709","tid":552531,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T11:11:37.000Z","msg":"同2"},{"pid":"29783e12db761357027d16c6f326ef76df3929a3","tid":552531,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T11:18:36.000Z","msg":"落棺蛇爆力救市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa44567f23ec26e1cad6b938bfa87d4452d3b16a","tid":552531,"uid":122566,"li